Sentencas: The apatite-type lanthanum silicate films were successfully synthesized by modified atmosphere plasma spraying using lanthanum oxide and silicon oxide mixed powders and precalcined hypereutectic powders in the size range 1-3 mu m and 5-8 mu m, respectively, as starting feedstock materials.
Titulo: Plasma spray synthesis of La10(SiO4)6O3 as a new electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The films differed not only in microstructural scale, but also in the characteristic of the degree of film densification.
Titulo: Plasma spray synthesis of La10(SiO4)6O3 as a new electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A detail describing the evolution of microstructure has been discussed.
Titulo: Plasma spray synthesis of La10(SiO4)6O3 as a new electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A considerable improvement in densification of the La-10(SiO4)(6)O-3 electrolyte films has been observed.
Titulo: Plasma spray synthesis of La10(SiO4)6O3 as a new electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
